<emphasis bold="true" box="[1424,1436,575,596]" pageId="2" pageNumber="524">4</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,399,1302]" box="[151,1436,605,627]" pageId="2" pageNumber="524">
<keyLead box="[151,1436,605,627]" pageId="2" pageNumber="524">
– Pronotal sculpture consisting of fine polygonal cells with large central grains; subparallel species (Figs 3,5,15).......... 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1424,1436,605,626]" pageId="2" pageNumber="524">3</emphasis>
